POST {{base_url}}/exercise-log
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "exercise_name": "Invalid Exercise",
  "exercise_type": "invalid_type",
  "duration_minutes": 30,
  "exercise_date": "2024-01-15"
}

###

# Create Invalid Exercise Log - Negative Duration
POST {{base_url}}/exercise-log
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "exercise_name": "Invalid Exercise",
  "exercise_type": "cardio",
  "duration_minutes": -10,
  "exercise_date": "2024-01-15"
}

###

# Create Invalid Exercise Log - Wrong Date Format
POST {{base_url}}/exercise-log
